reviewText: This publication is not for sale and can be viewed and downloaded for free on jw.org: http://www.jw.org/en/publications/videos/preach-to-ends-of-earth/

Go to jw dot org
at the top click on publications
then on the left click on videos
arrow through until you find it

Seller appears to breaking the law because JW's do not sell any of their products.

Any genuinely interested party may view this video or any other produced by 'Watchtower Bible and Tract Society of New York, Inc.' without charge, by contacting a Jehovah,s Witness or contacting the relevant headquarters.

If you were to read the back of the VHS cover it should say "All rights are reserved".
It is also available on DVD, but is not for sale as should be stated on the back cover of the dvd.

Or may be this is a pirated copy.

Don't let the seller take you for a fool.
